data.content: Second attempt: replaced top-level zsh grouping logic to use explicit compadd groups in generated _kno_commands/_kno__help_commands (compadd -V common-commands / other-commands with -X '%B%F{cyan}...%f%b' headers), instead of relying on _describe + zstyle grouping behavior. Removed injected zstyle dependency for these sections. Local validation: cargo test completions::tests::zsh_ passes and generated script parses with zsh -n. Awaiting user runtime verification.
